    "Afterward, we assign labels to the clusters and extract named entities from each cluster to display how the entire process operates on a fresh dataset.",
    "Literature reviewCTs have become an increasingly prevalent part of public discourse in recent years, fueled largely by the rise of social media platforms.",
    "As false narratives can negatively impact civic discourse and public health decisions, there is a pressing need to develop automated solutions for detecting conspiratorial content at scale.",
